                     <interp inst="t18650508-575-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>, Feloniously forging an order for the pay-ment of 14<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 7<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., with intent to defraud, <hi rend="italic">second count</hi>, uttering.</rs>
